{"_id":"2177c28d-f473-45c9-9cb5-138b96986d3e","type":"ability","name":"Exploit Weakness","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Exploit Weakness","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"fast","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"When you have successfully used Sense Weakness on a person in your current Venture, you may exploit this weakness in conversation or in combat to deal Heavy Inuition damage or to grant them Vulnerability to one of your attacks. This may only be used once per person.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"27798690-8f42-41af-8d0f-caed02dfdad0","type":"ability","name":"Betray Trust","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Betray Trust","rank":"5","type":"technique","action":"weapon","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"When you attack a foe who is not expecting your attack, you may use your Guile skill to make the attack. The attack does Heavy damage regardless of the weapon used.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vigour","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"2e74cdaf-ba6c-4146-8e42-41e5ffaecd9d","type":"ability","name":"Until Proven Otherwise","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Until Proven Otherwise","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You may use this ability when you lie, making your words completely believable --- you have no tells and give no hints to the fact that you are lying. So long as the lie is somewhat believable, those you have lied to act as though your words were entirely true (or at least give you the benefit of the doubt) without requiring a roll from you until they have proof otherwise. Note this does not compel them to behave differently --- even if the security guard believes you that you just forgot your ID today, she may not let you enter because it would contravene the bank's policy.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"44d416ae-5414-45cd-9fec-4e397dc20308","type":"ability","name":"Web of Lies","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Web of Lies","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"When caught in a lie, you may tell an even greater lie to attempt to cover it. On a success, you negate the consequences of your lie. On a failure, you take a Consequence in addition to any other consequences from your first lie.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"476bd548-c415-4430-88b9-081f9680aeee","type":"ability","name":"Veiled Words","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Veiled Words","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"When speaking to someone, even in front of many others, you can work in a basic message, threat, question, or similar without anyone else noticing.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"4f8db806-001e-4df1-934b-3ce1ab9474ee","type":"ability","name":"Taboo Topic","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Taboo Topic","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You can subtly shift the topic of conversation away from something you would rather avoid, or lie by omission. On a success, the target is unaware of what you have done. On a failure, they become suspicious of you and you take one Consequence, but they do not react as poorly as though you had explicitly lied to them.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"784ada7c-e33e-45fd-9ace-ac7aaffe69af","type":"ability","name":"Not Buying It","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Not Buying It","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You may use this ability on someone you believe is lying to you or conning you. Make a check vs their Intuition. If you succeed, they take Heavy Intuition damage (though this cannot result in Wounds) and you gain a Boon on all interactions with them until the end of the Venture. If you fail, or they are not lying, you instead take a Consequence.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"a2cd4ae8-4c17-4da9-954d-b1b334326940","type":"ability","name":"Talk in Circles","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Talk in Circles","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"When you spend at least a minute talking to someone, you can easily confuse them. On a success, they take Standard Intelligence damage. On a failure, they realize what you are up to and a Consequence is added to the tracker.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"a932dd31-5a19-4df0-8a96-cc968bea5377","type":"ability","name":"Polygraph","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Polygraph","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"3","description":"You may use this to know whether someone is lying to you or holding back information. No roll is required.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"af40de47-3f0c-450f-876c-d8361c132cef","type":"ability","name":"Distraction","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Distraction","rank":"1","type":"technique","action":"medium","defense":"","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"Next","cost":"1","description":"You can hinder enemies in combat. The next time the foe makes any check, roll your skill die. Subtract the value from their result.","roll_type":"Help","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"c644a3da-a2bb-4684-a21d-5eeec9e4d7b5","type":"skill","name":"Guile","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill_id":"guile","domain":"Expertise","rank":1,"stat":"intuition","description":"The Guile skill is used to con or deceive others as well as to know when you are being conned or deceived. It can also be used to navigate delicate social situations deftly or to manipulate others."}}
{"_id":"d60e7661-7927-44d7-aa6d-65629838c17e","type":"ability","name":"Point Fingers","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Point Fingers","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"This ability can be used when you would take a Consequence from interacting with someone, or from someone observing your actions. You attempt to direct the blame on a specific person, negating the Consequence on a success. It must be within the realm of posibility for that person to be to blame. On a failure you instead take another Consequence.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
{"_id":"d890cbeb-321d-404e-af22-5f8fb8b4f290","type":"ability","name":"Sense Weakness","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/guile.svg","system":{"skill":"Guile","name":"Sense Weakness","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"If you spend at least ten minutes talking to someone, you can get a sense of their weaknesses, such as their fears, vices, or insecurities. You also learn what they will find most believable, and gain a Boon to deceive them or sense deception in them. If you fail your check they become suspicious of you and the GM will add a Consequence to the tracker.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"guile"}}
